items.preview:
COYOTES (13-17-5) at PANTHERS (16-18-4)

7 p.m. ET; BSFL, BSAZ, ESPN+, SN NOW

items.title: Keller scores goal
items.description: Clayton Keller scores against the Florida Panthers to make it 2-2

items.title: Staal scores on a rebound
items.blurb: ARI@FLA: Staal puts home a goal to extend lead
items.description: Eric Staal picks up the puck on a rebound and shoots from the circle to extend the Panthers' lead to 2-0

items.title: Tkachuk nets opening goal
items.blurb: ARI@FLA: Tkachuk scores an early 1st period goal
items.description: Matthew Tkachuk gets a feed from Aleksander Barkov and puts it home to put the Panthers on the board 1 minute into the 1st period

items.title: Chychrun fires home PPG
items.blurb: ARI@FLA: Chychrun puts Coyotes on the board with PPG
items.description: Jakob Chychrun gets a feed from Clayton Keller and gets in tight to score a power-play goal, making it 2-1 in the final seconds of the 1st
